title: St. Hyacinth's Church, Wierzbica Górna
text: St. Hyacinth's Church in <a href="Wierzbica%20G%C3%B3rna">Wierzbica Górna</a> (<a href="Gmina%20Wo%C5%82czyn">Gmina Wołczyn</a>), Poland, is a <a href="wood">wood</a>en church built in 1722. The church belongs to St. <a href="Hyacinth%20of%20Poland">Hyacinth</a> Parish in <a href="Wierzbica%20G%C3%B3rna">Wierzbica Górna</a>, in the <a href="Namys%C5%82%C3%B3w">Namysłów</a>-South <a href="Deanery">Deanery</a> of the <a href="Roman%20Catholic%20Archdiocese%20of%20Wroc%C5%82aw">Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Wrocław</a>. Since April 18, 1964 the church was registered on the <a href="Register%20of%20objects%20of%20cultural%20heritage">Register of Objects of Cultural Heritage</a> for the <a href="Opole%20Voivodeship">Opole Voivodeship</a>, with the registration number of 818/64.
